data.title: A summer of live music just waiting for Ravens offensive line to come around
data.meta_description: Dennis Koulatsos and Nestor discuss the long view of a summer of pure concert joy, getting off the boulevard of last year's broken sports dreams and being a basket case until the Ravens' offensive line is ready to run the ball.
